description:
The Motorola moto g Stylus (2023) from Tracfone is the phone with all the tools you need to stay in focus and on point. With the featured built-in stylus, you can jot notes, edit photos, sketch artwork, and navigate effortlessly with pinpoint precision. The 50MP Quad Pixel camera system allows you to capture sharp and bright photos even in the most challenging light and never worry about recharging, thanks to a 5000mAh battery. Plus, with Dolby Atmos audio you can immerse yourself in multidimensional sound, listening with improved bass, cleaner vocals, and more clarity than ever before.

With Tracfone now you're in control with no contracts and stay connected with reliable nationwide 4G and 5G coverage. Enjoy unlimited talk & text, plus Unlimited Carryover Data* that never expires so you can get the most from your wireless plan.

To activate this device, a Tracfone plan is required. To find the Tracfone Plans available to purchase, please go to our TF - Amazon Brand Page linked below the product title.

5G access requires a 5G-capable device in a 5G coverage area.
*Service must be active and in use within any six-month period.
